CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, pg. A12 reads: " Planning Big Things - Members of the newly organized Los Jovenes Missionary Club of Trinity AME Church map their first church aid project. Seated, left to right, Jean Brown, Sylvia Wilson, Vivian Hedgeman and Jo Ann Dickerson.  Rear, left to right, Barbara Nevels, Mary Stevens, president; Joseph Wilkins, William Smith, Ann Lois Hicks, Ann Sells, Beverly Sewell and Kenneth Nelson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Los Jovenes Missionary Club members seated from left: Jean Brown, Sylvia Wilson, Vivian Hedgeman, Jo Ann Dickerson; rear: Barbara Nevels, Mary Stevens, Joseph Wilkins, William Smith, Ann Lois Hicks, Ann Sells, Beverly Sewell, and Kenneth Nelson gathered in Trinity AME Church
